        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 13–21. LM. F. lacrima. Valve views showing the size diminution series for specimens from Brasil. Figure 19 is the holotype. Note the large degree of variation in valve shape among specimens. Scale bar: 10 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894845/files/figure.png" .

